{"tid":665411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(當今聖上?) 人民日報：不少腐敗官員童年貧苦、中年上升、終落得晚年悲慘","createTime":"2018-05-15T02:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T05:28:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e218c7860dc61b3df848677eb241f5691cc44fc8","tid":665411,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"中共十九大後，中央反腐的姿態仍然強硬。而內地官媒《人民日報》今日亦刊文批評，腐敗的官員表面上是對財物的貪婪，實際是精神上的貧血。<br />\n<br />\n據《人民日報》今日一篇社評指出，不少腐敗官員都有着「貧苦的童年」，經過「奮鬥的青年」、「上升的中年」，最終卻落得個「悲慘的晚年」。他們在權力加身後逐漸喪失初心，他們不是忍受不了貧窮的困苦，而是抵制不住誘惑的「糖衣」。他們「不能忍窮，『貧』字多一『點』，就會走向『貪』」。<br />\n<br />\n文章表示，有的腐敗分子看到一些商人生活奢華，「忍窮力」未能抵住誘惑力，想「追求像他們一樣的生活」，最終就「如初食鴉片一般不能自拔，一步步走向罪惡的深淵」。此外，文中又指有部份黨員幹部隨着職務升遷，因而面對更多掌聲、誘惑和圍獵，他們能否保持「不忘初心、方得始終」的清醒，不貪圖權力背後的名利地位，是避免「成名每在窮苦日，敗事多因得志時」的關鍵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/186855/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%E8%85%90%E6%95%97%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B4%E8%B2%A7%E8%8B%A6-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E7%B5%82%E8%90%BD%E5%BE%97%E6%99%9A%E5%B9%B4%E6%82%B2%E6%85%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F186855%2F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25A0%25B1-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%2591%25E8%2585%2590%25E6%2595%2597%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E8%258B%25A6-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%2587-%25E7%25B5%2582%25E8%2590%25BD%25E5%25BE%2597%25E6%2599%259A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2582%25B2%25E6%2585%2598&d=19Onf4KoFeeu3uVua%2B1FOsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=f851c93f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/186855/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E5%A0%B1-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%91%E8%85%90%E6%95%97%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B4%E8%B2%A7%E8%8B%A6-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E7%B5%82%E8%90%BD%E5%BE%97%E6%99%9A%E5%B9%B4%E6%82%B2%E6%85%98</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fed8e844273a9eea2954562f23457f6f29443b","tid":665411,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899b8f2058591a471c1ec1fa5a89650b02fda713","tid":665411,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}